  <brief_title>Preventive Effect of Treatment With Estradiol Vaginal Tablets on Recurrent Urinary Tract Infections in Post-menopausal Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>Preventive Effect of Treatment With Estradiol Vaginal Tablets on Recurrent Urinary Tract Infections in Post-menopausal Women (RUTI) in Post-menopausal Women With Signs of Urogenital Ageing (UGA)</official_title>
