  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Europe. The aim of this trial is to investigate the preventive
      effect of treatment with estradiol vaginal tablets on recurrent urinary tract infections
      (RUTI) in post-menopausal women with signs of urogenital ageing (UGA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
