  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Post-menopausal woman with Urogenital ageing (UGA)

          -  Recurrent urinary tract infections defined as three or more urinary tract infections
             within the past twelve months

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Known or suspected allergy to trial product or related products

          -  Present UTI

          -  History of RUTI during fertile period of life
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
